"Día Nacional de la Memoria"     weekend on march 24
"Viernes Santo"                  weekend on easter minus 2
"Día de los Caídos en Malvinas"  weekend on april 2
"Día del Trabajador"             weekend on may 1
"Primer Gobierno Patrio"         weekend on may 25
"Día de Manuel Belgrano"         weekend on third monday in june
"Día de la Independencia"        weekend on july 9
"Día de San Martín"              weekend on third monday in august
"Día de la Raza"                 weekend on ( ([10/12] == [tuesday after ([10/11])] || [10/12] == [wednesday after ([10/11])]) ?
                                              [monday before ([10/12])] :
                                              [monday after  ([10/11])] )
"Inmaculada Concepción de María" weekend on december 8
"Navidad"                        weekend on december 25

